Usage: reportRoute [-help] [-clock] [-em] [-ndr] [-selected_net_only]
                   [-via_pillar]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-clock                 # report short wires statistics of clock nets
                       # (bool, optional)
-em                    # report EM statistics of nets (bool, optional)
-ndr                   # report NDR statistics of nets (bool, optional)
-selected_net_only     # report statistics of selected nets (bool, optional)
-via_pillar            # call report_stacking_via cmd (bool, optional)